            <div class="faq-card c6"><h3>Can I use it on a Mac?</h3><p>Yes. Because it runs in a browser, it works on Mac, Windows, and any device with a modern browser and microphone.</p></div>
            <div class="faq-card c6"><h3>How does it compare to Dragon for heavy daily dictation?</h3><p>Dragon Professional is better suited for heavy daily dictation with deep Windows integration, custom macros, and offline capability. SpeechRecognition.cloud suits professionals who need flexibility across devices and locations.</p></div>
